<plot>Stanley Wyatt, a talented successful artist, leading a solitary, contemplative existence. His art, as his life, is devoid of colour and excitement, until Helen moves in next door. From that point on, Stanley begins to introduce new ideas into his work, which changes his direction. Eventually, he re-examines his past and learns that is is never too late to adapt to change.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?394630</url></doc>
